OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who was portrayed in a film as a 
OL,6, life-saving hero during the Rwandan    
OL,7, genocide has been convicted of         
OL,8, terrorism by a court in Rwanda.        
OL,10,FPaul Rusesabagina was found guilty of  
OL,11,Fbacking a rebel group from exile which 
OL,12,Fkilled civilians in attacks in 2018.   
OL,14,FHis family have alleged that he was    
OL,15,Ftaken to Rwanda by force. They also say
OL,16,Fthat he did not have a fair trial.     
OL,18,FRusesabagina's journey from celebrated 
OL,19,Ffigure to state enemy happened as his  
OL,20,Fcriticism of the government grew.      
